<div class="abouttext large-12 columns">
  <h1>HASHTAT</h1>
  <p class="top">
    is a community for tattoo art and the stories behind the ink. We're three art-loving women who learned to code in 10 weeks, culminating in hashtat.com. We attended Austin's first development bootcamp,
      <a href="http://www.themakersquare.com">MakerSquare</a>, and didn't know a lick of code prior to the experience.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="row pics">
  <div class="large-4 columns">
    <div class="avatar tina">
      <%= image_tag("ctina.gif") %>
      <p>Tina</p>
      <p class="bio">
        Full Stack Merge Master
        <br/>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="large-4 columns">
    <div class="shannon avatar">
      <%= image_tag("cshannon.gif") %>
      <p>Shannon</p>
      <p class="bio">
        The Back End Beast
        <br/>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="large-4 columns">
    <div class="doa avatar">
      <%= image_tag("cdoa.gif") %>
      <p>Doa</p>
      <p class="bio">
        The Front End Freak
        <br/>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="subtext large-6 columns">
  <h1>THANKS</h1>
  <p>
    We stand on the shoulders of the patient teachers, mentors and coders who believed in us and inspire us to keep building.
    <p>
      Many thanks to the MKS founders and our classmates, Micah Frazier, Aaron Scruggs,  Matthew Buck, Mike Ornellas, Nathaniel Jones, Gilbert Garza, Christina Day, Scott Bellware, Mando Escamilla, Damon Clinkscales, Sam Kapila, Nick Zadrozny, and Andres Angulo.
    </p>
  </p>
</div>
<div class="subtext large-offset-1 columns large-5 columns">
  <h1>CONTACT</h1>
  <p>
    We built HashTat for you, so when it comes to your feedback, we're all ears. Let us know if you found a bug, if you have ideas to make the site better, or just to say hi.
    <p>
      Tweet us @mrhashtat or shoot an e-mail to
        <a href="mailto:mrhashtat@gmail.com">mrhashtat@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </p>
</div>

